caption:
✏️ I will never stop learning - taking the time and budgeting to take in person trainings is a top priority when you love your craft. 

I started lashing in December 2017 - and have taken over 15 trainings since. 

This incredible styling training was one I have sought after for years! Training with Mel from @glitzlashstudio - was mind blowing. 

So thankful for those who spent the day taking in new education with me : @hair_and_lashes_by_keira @emilyelizabeththeestie @syracuselashes @eyesofenvy_ @makeuplove_cny
